.bid.box(style='text-align: left')
	h1 Privacy Policy

	p
		| Before you continue to use our service, please read and agree
		| to #[a(href='/privacy-policy', target='_blank') our Privacy Policy]
		| (the link opens in a new tab).

	.row
		.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
			form(role='login', action='', method='POST')
				| {% csrf_token %}
				| {{ form.next_url }}
				fieldset
					| {{ form.agree }}
					label(style='display: inline', for='{{ form.agree.id_for_label }}')
						| I have read and agree to the privacy policy as linked above.

					.bid-cta
						button.btn-success(type='submit') Submit &amp; Continue
						| {% if may_skip and form.next_url.value %}
						a.button.btn-warning(style='margin-left: 1em', href='{{ form.next_url.value }}') Â» Skip for now
						| {% endif %}

	h2(style='margin-top: 2em') Our policy in three points

	ul
		li
			| We value your privacy.
		li
			| We only ask for personal information needed to run this service,
			| namely your full name, email address, and nickname.
		li
			| We will not share your personal information with third parties,
			| unless you use Blender ID to log in at a third-party website.

	p.note
		| Note that these three points do not consistute a legally binding text. For that,
